column4: <content>Gillis Mostaert paintings comparable to Dr. Becker's painting: Faggin. 1) Peasants attacked -Louvre 42 x 69 cm; 2) Destruction of Sodom with Lot & Daughters led by the Angel 26 x 35 (De Boer, Adv.); 3) (*)Lot & Daughters escaping from Sodom - Finck (Brussels) colour reproduction in Witt Library 32,8 x 46 (Photo needed); 4) Lot & Daughters escaping from Sodom Brussels, Museum 50,5 x 66,5 cm; 5) Destruction of Sodom with Lot & Daughters in cave, Dr. Schapiro 11 3/4 x 16in.; 6) (*) Destruction of Sodom with monogram, Paris (Drouot), 6-12-1965, cat. N° 128 illustrat. (mentioned by [Giorgio T.] Faggin, [La pittura ad Anversa nel cinquecento, Florence: Marchi & Bertolli], 1968, p. 82, n. 41. Not seen. Not in Witt Library-possible RKDH, from where photo to be requested. Finck & Schapiro closest to Becker.</content>
